$interpreted:
Jerome: First row, archers, advance!
Second row, foot soldiers, follow up!
Jerome: Good! That's it for today's practice. Line up!
Jerome: Hey, who's position is that?

Sharice: R, Report...
T, the G.O.A.T, Sharice Carterwell, is here... Huff... Puff...

Jerome: Carterwell, you're late!
Did nobody tell you the time of today's morning practice?
Sharice: (If I told him that indeed nobody told me about the time, I'll probably be ostracized even further...)
Sharice: Haha, I overslept~
Sharice: Besides, I'm the greatest after all; no need for mundane practices like this. I'm on a totally different level than these...
Jerome: Are you stupid or what!
Jerome: Don't be full of yourself! Just because you beat the monsters at Maple Lake by accident doesn't mean you can disobey orders!
Jerome: Run thirty laps after we're done here!
Sharice: Why should I, it's not like I purposely...
Jerome: You got something to say, Carterwell?
Sharice: No Sir!

Sharice: Pfft, thirty laps? That's a piece of cake. 
I'll do forty laps! Hahahaha!

Grouchy Soldier: Ha, serves her right. 
She deserves to get screwed anyway, with all that cocky behavior...
Jerome: A monster? Everyone, keep the formation tight! Archers...
Sharice: No need for that. All of you, back off! I'll hand the monster myself!
Sharice: See~ Without me, all of you would be long dead~

Sharice: (Everyone should be able to accept me now, right... 
If they realize how strong I am...)

Jerome: Sharice Carterwell!
How many times do I have to scold you before you learn to obey orders!
Sharice: Umm.... but
Cruel Soldier: Arrogant dumb***...
Grouchy Soldier: Just ignore her. Let's go.
Sharice: Hey, weaklings, wait for me...
Jerome: I'm not done chewing you out yet. Stay where you are, and stand straight!

Sharice: I've been trying so hard already...
Why... just why... is it not working...
